s3 = {1, 2, 3, 5, 6, 7}

print(" Disjoint set is :",s1.isdisjoint(s2))
print(" Subjoint set is :",s1.issubset(s2))
print(" Supjoint set is :",s3.issuperset(s1))
</code></pre> Output<pre><code>Disjoint set is : False
